c: 2
v: 60
t: "Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kajwaŵendele Musa ŵandu ŵakwe mesi, nitwantesile kuti: “Putasyani simbo jenujo peganga.” Basi nisyaumile mwalakwemo sulo likumi kwisa siŵili, mwanti lukosyo lulilose lwamanyilile pakumwela pakwe. (Twasalile kuti): “Lyagani soni mwagani mu lisiki lyampele Allah, nambo nkalapwaga pa chilambo pakuwatanganya"